descriptionHtml:
🏠 The official app for 99.co Singapore, the fastest growing property portal in Singapore 🏠

Get access to Singapore’s fastest growing property portal, with more than 100,000 listings in Singapore to buy and rent in one app. With thousands of HDB flats, condos, landed houses, and commercial properties, find your ideal home here on 99.co. Unsure where to start looking? View our Must See and Verified Listings where we curate authentic listings for you.

Our app offers you all you need at every step of your home-buying or home-renting process.
With our powerful location search, you can now search for listings with these smart filters:
✅ District (E.g. District 18 - Tampines, Pasir Ris)
✅ MRT stations
✅ Schools nearby
✅ Travel time and distance
✅ Price, psf price
✅ Number of bedrooms, bathrooms
✅ Floor size, level
✅ Tenure, build year

📍Exclusive feature: It is even easier for you to use 99.co with our draw-map feature to specify your ideal location.

After you have shortlisted your listings, contact the agent representatives directly with just a click, or share the listings with your friends and family via SMS, email, Whatsapp, etc.

99.co key features:
🔍 Smart search filters: Search for your ideal property by price, location, psf price, MRT, number of bedrooms, bathrooms, floor size, tenure, build year, floor level, etc

🔔 Personalised alerts: Set up notifications or alerts for new listings that match your search criteria

🏢 Discover new launch projects: Learn more about the latest new launch condo or upcoming projects and developments

📰 Access to latest property news: Read property news and market insights on the go

📈Property value: Calculate the value of your property on the app, which is powered by X-Value

Finding a property for sale or rent? Download 99.co now to find #YourWayHome

About us:
99.co is a part of 99 Group. 99 Group is a regional property technology startup with a vision to empower home-seekers and make property search smarter and easier. 99 Group is currently headquartered in Singapore and it is currently operational in Singapore and Indonesia.

In Singapore, 99 Group operates 99.co, SRX.com.sg, while in Indonesia, it operates 99.co/id and Rumah123.com.

Visit our website to find out more about 99 Group: https://www.99.co/about-us
